Pedionis (Pedionis) 
<taxonomicName box="[504,596,1925,1948]" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" rank="species" species="yunnana" status="sp. nov.">yunnana</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[602,685,1925,1948]" pageId="6" pageNumber="59" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
A, pygophore, subgenital plates, lateral view; B, style, lateral view; C, aedeagus, dorsal connective, lateral view; D, aedeagus and dorsal connectives, caudal view; E, connective, lateral view; F, connective, dorsal view.
</paragraph>
